This is the software for the Bricktronics projects.

Bricktronics - The Arduino library for the Bricktronics Shield, Bricktronics Megashield, and Bricktronics Motor Driver. This is now a combined library, instead of having separate libraries for each board.

Releases - Contains ZIP archives of the Bricktronics library above, released on specific dates. Mostly for historical interest. Includes the original split-library designs.

DrummerBot - An Arduino sketch for a cool project featured in a Make Magazine blog post.

